{
  "id": "adv_card_ski_52_02",
  "title": "白石沙季",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――旅館　ロビー",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.0333333373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ふわあ……なんだか変な時間に起きてしまったな\nまだ明け方だしもうひと眠りでも……",
      "startTime": 9.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 13.0333333373
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　あそこにいるのは……\nおーい沙季、こんな朝早くにどこか出掛けるのか？",
      "startTime": 17.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.2
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0666655262
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さん。おはようございます\nこれから神社巡りに行くんです",
      "startTime": 25.9666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.866666162
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "京都には沢山の神社があるので、様々なご利益を\nいただくために早めに出発しないといけないんです",
      "startTime": 32.5333339691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "へえ、そんなに沢山あるのか。さすが京都だな\n沙季はどんな神社に行く予定なんだ？",
      "startTime": 41.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.5333328287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "……無病息災、厄除け、学問成就、芸能上達の神社に\n商売繁盛、不老長寿、良縁の神社と――",
      "startTime": 49.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "後は、美人祈願の神社には絶対に行く予定です\n今日のために完璧なスケジュールを計画してきました",
      "startTime": 57.6666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.4666641276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "す、凄い数の神社に行くんだな……\nでも、商売繁盛と厄除けは俺も行っておきたいな",
      "startTime": 65.0999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.4999974609
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "そうですか。じゃあ、{user}さんも行きましょう\nさっそく出発……",
      "startTime": 72.7999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そうだ。朝ごはんでも食べてから行かないか？\n近くに有名な店があるみたいなんだが……",
      "startTime": 77.8333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.666662093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "……ダメです",
      "startTime": 80.666662093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "え？",
      "startTime": 81.766662093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.566662093
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_onsenlobby-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "onsenlobby-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.3666646322
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "今すぐ出発します。見て下さい、このスケジュール\n一分一秒も無駄に出来ないんです",
      "startTime": 86.5999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "三分後のバスに乗れなかったらスケジュールが\n全部狂ってしまいます！　さあ、走りますよ！",
      "startTime": 91.9666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええ……！？",
      "startTime": 95.5666646362,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3066.6666627000013,
          "startTime": 98.6333312989
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 98.01665955
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 98.01665955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "なんとかスケジュール通りに着きましたね\nここは人気なので人が少ない早朝に来たかったんです",
      "startTime": 105.2999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 109.766653955
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "厄除けにご利益がある神社らしいですよ\nはい、{user}さん。これをどうぞ",
      "startTime": 113.2666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 116.2333206217
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こ、これは……こんにゃく？\nいつの間に……",
      "startTime": 119.9666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "さっき買ってきました。これを本殿の方を向いて黙って\n食べながら願い事をすると、叶うと言われているんです",
      "startTime": 125.8666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 129.966653955
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 134.3333312989
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski012.m4a",
      "text": "さっそく食べましょう！　えっと、あっちを向いて……\nもにゅ……月ストが……もにゅ……千紗に……もにゅ",
      "startTime": 136.1333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 136.1333312989
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 149.5999979656
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "沙季……真剣なところ悪いんだが\n心の声が漏れてるぞ……",
      "startTime": 150.7999979656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 152.8999872883
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski013.m4a",
      "text": "……！　いけません、もう一度やり直します！\n黙って食べないとご利益を受けられませんから！",
      "startTime": 156.8666646322,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11999.99898279998,
          "startTime": 168.866663615
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 161.4333226561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "お参りも終わったし、ちょっと境内を回ってみるか\nあ、おみくじがあるぞ、沙季。やってみるか？",
      "startTime": 166.766663615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 170.766658024
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski014.m4a",
      "text": "わ、私は大丈夫です",
      "startTime": 170.766658024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_shrine-01-noon",
      "startTime": 173.5999969483
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "沙季？　そわそわしているみたいだが大丈夫か？\nこんにゃくを食べ過ぎてお腹が痛いとか……",
      "startTime": 178.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-ski015.m4a",
      "text": "違います！　次の神社に行くためのバスの時間が\nそろそろなので……",
      "startTime": 185.5426776064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ski_52_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "もう行くのか？　まだ来たばかりだし\nもう少しゆっくりしても――",
      "startTime": 190.7999938965,
      "sfxList": []
    },
